```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B["Generate a random number within the specified range"]
    B --> C["Prompt user for a guess"]
    C --> D["Check if input is valid (numeric and within range)"]
    D -- "Invalid input" --> E["Display error message"]
    E --> C
    D -- "Valid input" --> F["Compare guess to the target number"]
    F -- "Guess too high" --> G["Inform user the guess is too high"]
    G --> C
    F -- "Guess too low" --> H["Inform user the guess is too low"]
    H --> C
    F -- "Correct guess" --> I["Congratulate the user"]
    I --> J([End])
```
